1. *Ostavljaj* knjigu na stolu. (Leave the book on the table.)
2. Kada *ostavljate* svoju decu kod bake i deke, uvek proverite da li su tamo lekovi. (When you leave your children with grandma and grandpa, always check if there are any medicines there.)
3. *Ostavljajući* svoju prošlost iza sebe, ona je krenula napred. (By leaving her past behind, she moved forward.)
4. Neću te *ostaviti*. (I won't leave you.)
5. Ona me je *ostavila* zbog drugog muškarca. (She left me for another man.)
6. Molim te, *ostavi* me na miru. (Please, leave me alone.)
7. *Ostavio* sam svoj novčanik u taksiju. (I left my wallet in the taxi.)
8. On je *ostavio* neizbrisiv trag u svetu nauke. (He left an indelible mark in the world of science.)
9. *Ostavljena* deca su veoma ranjiva. (Abandoned children are very vulnerable.)
10. Nemoj *ostavljati* prljave sudove u sudoperi. (Don't leave dirty dishes in the sink.)